    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Check Your Redesign \r\n\r\nUse this AI chat space to evaluate your redesign idea from the user's perspective.\r\n\r\n<br/> \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n**Step 1:** Choose Files\r\n\r\nFrom the library, upload or select:\r\n- The app wireframe that matches your redesign\r\n- The user empathy map you want to focus on\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n**Step 2**: Describe Your Change\r\n\r\nIn the chat, briefly explain:\r\n- What problem or vulnerability you were trying to solve\r\n- What you added, removed, or changed to improve it\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n**Step 3:** Ask for Feedback\r\n\r\nPick a question below to test your redesign:\r\n\r\n- How would this user react to my changes?\r\n- How does my redesign change how this user shares personal info?\r\n- How does my redesign make this feature more secure or trustworthy?\r\n- Does it help the user feel more in control?\r\n- What if it didn't work as expected?\r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "submittable": "false",
